The '''2016 [[World Rugby Under 20 Trophy]]''' was the ninth annual international rugby union competition for Under 20 national teams, second-tier world championship.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldrugby.org/news/89540|title=Zimbabwe to host World Rugby U20 Trophy 2016|date=7 September 2015|publisher=worldrugby.org|accessdate=8 September 2015}}</ref>

The event was held in [[Harare]], [[Zimbabwe]] and was organized by rugby's governing body, [[World Rugby]].

