== Qualifying ==
As the host nation, Zimbabwe qualified automatically, as did [[Samoa national under-20 rugby union team|Samoa]] for being relegated from [[2015 World Rugby Under 20 Championship]]. The remaining six countries competed through a qualification process in their regional competitions (Africa, Asia, North America, South America and Europe).

