The '''Hungarian motorcycle Grand Prix''' was a motorcycling event that had been part of the [[Grand Prix motorcycle racing]] World Championship.
Only two editions were held, and despite efforts to engineer a return in [[2010 Grand Prix motorcycle racing season|2010]] at the [[Balatonring]] circuit, the race did not take place and was replaced on the calendar by the [[Aragon motorcycle Grand Prix]].
