The '''Stade Gaston Peyrille''' is a stadium primarily used for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches in [[Bitam]], [[Gabon]]. It is the home of the Gabonese team [[US Bitam]] of the [[Gabon Championnat National D1]]. The stadium has capacity of 7,000 spectators.

